               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgGeo5\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGeo5', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: In this map, the continent is highlighted © Mapswire (<htcite0>)</p>",
               "source": [
